    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a reliable daily driver for someone who isn't concerned with cosmetic perfection. The exterior has some noticeable scratches and minor dings consistent with its age, and the interior shows moderate wear on the upholstery. Mechanically, the car starts and runs well, though it will likely need a tune-up and new tires in the near future. It\u2019s a solid, functional vehicle that has been maintained regularly, even if it shows its history on the surface.",
