    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b I am so excited to show you this absolute gem! It is honestly in stunning condition\u2014practically like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, so the interior is spotless and the ride is as smooth as can be. It\u2019s been my pride and joy, but it\u2019s time for it to find a new home where it\u2019ll be just as loved. If you're looking for a ride that looks and feels brand new, you've found it! Feel free to reach out with any questions! \u2728",
      "price": 43900.0,
